Package com.intellij.openapi.fileEditor.impl

Class EditorComposite

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.fileEditor.impl.EditorComposite
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Disposable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EditorWithProviderComposite

    public class EditorComposite
extends java.lang.Object
implements Disposable
    This class hides internal structure of UI component which represent set of opened editors. For example, one myEditor is represented by its component, more then one myEditor is wrapped into tabbed pane.
